---
title: Double Chicken Korma Curry & Onion Chutney with Baby Broccoli & Garlic Rice
description: There's nothing like a mildly-spiced chicken korma curry topped with onion chutney for a warming weeknight meal. Make sure to use the fluffy rice to soak up all that delicious curry sauce!

